## FastAPI Rules

### API Design
- Use RESTful conventions for endpoints
- Group related endpoints using APIRouter
- Use proper HTTP status codes
- Include comprehensive error handling using method in exceptions.py
- Use dependency injection for database sessions and authentication
- Implement proper request/response models with Pydantic

### Endpoint Naming
- Use plural nouns for resource collections: `/products/`, `/categories/`
- Use specific actions for non-CRUD operations: `/products/{id}/activate`
- Version APIs: `/api/v1/products/`

### Error Handling
- Use appropriate HTTP status codes
- Return detailed error messages
- Include error codes for automated handling
- Log all errors with request context
- Handle validation errors consistently